### Place Order from Cart (Customer)
### Creates a new order from cart items
### Items are automatically grouped by seller into separate seller orders
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "source": "CART",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "sellerId": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "customerName": "Ahmed Mohamed",
    "address": "15 El-Tahrir Street, Apt 4B, Dokki",
    "province": "Giza",
    "phone": "01012345678",
    "notes": "Please call before delivery"
  },
  "paymentMethod": "COD"
}


### Place Order Direct (Buy Now)
### Creates a new order directly without using cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "source": "DIRECT",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "sellerId": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "customerName": "Fatima Ali",
    "address": "25 Nile Street, Maadi",
    "province": "Cairo",
    "phone": "01098765432"
  },
  "paymentMethod": "COD"
}


### List Customer Orders
### Returns all orders for the authenticated customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Get Order by ID
### Returns a single order by its ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### List Seller Orders
### Returns all orders containing products from the authenticated seller
### Note: Must be logged in as a seller
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sellers/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
